info.about: A product photography studio specializing in pack shots for items such as apparel, jewelry, accessories, cosmetics, F&B, books, homewear & décor.
info.description:
A product photography studio specializing in high quality pack shots for items such as apparel, jewelry, accessories, cosmetics, F&B, books, homewear & décor. 

This is a perfect solution for business who are looking to create catalogues of their merchandize or display them online on their website or any other e-commerce sties. 

On average we can photograph between 30 to 50 items of your merchandize depending on the complexity of the item related to its design, color and material.

albums.title: On Model
albums.description:
This album contains a sample of product shots on a model that we have produced for our clients.  

We can photograph 30 items in 1 day depending on the complexity of items. Finalization usually takes additional 5 working days. 

E-mail us on info@raghunter.com or call on 01375035 / 70-855224 to ask for our Rate Card or more information.

albums.title: Apparel
albums.description:
This album contains a sample of product shots that we have produced for our clients. The item selection consists of Dresses, Tops, Shirts, Jackets, Coats, Skirts, Pants, Shorts. 

As you can see we photograph both women's and men's clothing and focus on creating a mannequin ghost effect when needed to better portray item's form and cut.

We usually photograph front, side, back and detail shots for apparel. Upon your request you can stick to one angle, several or ask us to shoot the item in a completely different way if you believe it will better portray your product. 

Up to date we have shot more than 2,000 apparel items which gave us a strong understanding of how light works with different material, color and pattern to produce hight quality pictures.  

We can photograph 30 items in 1 to 2 days depending on the complexity of items. Finalization usually takes additional 5 working days. 

E-mail us on info@raghunter.com or call on 01375035 / 70-855224 to ask for our Rate Card or more information.
